{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_SubEntityDeath}}
'''A_SubEntityDeath'''<br />
(no parameters)

A specialized variant of [[A_BossDeath]] that exits the level if there are no other living actors of the calling actor's type when called.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|EntitySecond}} and derived classes.

[[Category:Decorate Strife functions]] [[Category:Decorate Restricted functions]]{{DEFAULTSORT:SubEntityDeath}}
